items.bio: Digital Business Strategist, Speaker, Founder & Host of Web Wednesday, Asia's premier networking community for internet start-ups and digital media executives.
Chairman of I-COM Global, Scientist of life's finer moments
Chief Digital Officer, Dentsu APAC. Passionate about ideas that find audience, create participation & advance the users purpose.
Digital Marketing Strategist and Creative Director. Co-founder of social media content strategy tool Zuum.
Ex-scientist, ex-creative director, managing director, chairman, traveller, problem solver, husband, father, coffee quaffer and film buff
Digital Strategy Director, partner in a tech startup, writer, youth literacy advocate.  Cali-NYC hybrid.
At age 43, I was overworked & restless in a high-stress advertising career. So I sold all my worldly possessions & left on a trek around the world.  TheRobF.com
